TopicTitle: My Space Station series ... building using the MKS mod

Articles.Content:
Parts 1 -3  are edited and uploaded currently with a total of about 25 "filmed"  just need to edit and upload..... a new one every 2-3 days-ish 

It turns out to a be a pretty big, using 3.5m parts  -- most fully self sustaining  --  space station heavily using rover dudes  MKS mods       Tune in to see how it unfolds!

here's the first video and you can find the playlist from there.
